fields.name: The Great Barrier Reef Dive
fields.description: One of the greatest natural resources on Earth. See the amazing colours and biodiversity of this breathtaking vision of mothernature. This trip as well as being beautiful will also allow you to see what we're defending in the oceans. You'll also find out about another fight of the Barrier Reef and the bleaching of the coral due to climate change.

fields.name: Discovering the Cayman Islands
fields.description: You'll discover shipwrecks and amazing marine life on this dive. Turtles and Stingrays are also frequent in this part of the ocean. Two animals we've seen destroyed by plastics in our oceans. Mother Nature has given us some great gifts and we want more people to see what we're fighting for in all it's glory and wonder.

fields.name: The Madagascar Dive Adventure
fields.description: On this dive, we discover the wildlife and natural wonders of northern Madagascars oceans. This will include a liveaboard dive adventure exploring the reefs and stunning islands where you'll see giants of the ocean including whale sharks and humpback whales.
